About us

Bohdan is a brand creator who is always interested in making various things at home. He regularly experimented with different materials and tools, trying his hand at many fields, including candle making.

Soy wax is made from soybeans grown in Denmark, and this type of wax is environmentally friendly and safe for health.

Our goods

We use only the best quality materials: soy wax, wax dyes, high quality aromatic oils and cotton wicks. The shades of the candles are very harmoniously combined with the aroma, creating an unforgettable atmosphere in your home.
